CRPF Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 02 Psychologist and Other Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 29, 2025, 15:38 IST
 Central Reserve Police Force
 2 Jobs |  Posted On : 29-Aug-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 55,000 to 55,000




FOLLOW

The Central Reserve Police Force (CRPF) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 02 Psychologists, Nutritionist Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the M.Sc., Post-Graduation, can grab this chance and apply for the CRPF Recruitment 2025. Here, we mentioned the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible aspirants can attend the interview at the address given below.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more Jobs in Delhi.

CRPF Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Namwe of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Psychologist	01	Post Graduation
Nutritionist 	01	M.Sc

Age Limit for the CRPF Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years. 
The Maximum Age Limit: 50 years.

Selection Process for the CRPF Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the CRPF Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 55,000 /- per month.

Application fee for the CRPF Recruitment 2025

There is no application fee.
How to Apply for the CRPF Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Psychologist notification 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Then, attend the walk-in at the address given below.

Venue

Training Directorate, CRPF, East Block No. 10, Level 7, R K Puram, New Delhi, 110066

Important Dates

Date of Walk-in-Interview	09-10-2025
